subject: Tennis
United States Open (Tennis)
lead_paragraph: Fifth-seeded Nikolay Davydenko of Russia dispatched Dudi Sela of Israel, 6-3, 6-3, 6-3, while third-seeded Svetlana Kuznetsova defeated Sorana Cirstea to advance in the women’s bracket.
